            "en": "<p>You must pay a one-off fee for handling the application for recognition as ‘environmental expert in soil corrosion’.</p><ul><li>For <strong>2023</strong>, the one-off fee is <strong>681 </strong>euros.</li></ul><p>As a recognised ‘environmental expert in soil corrosion’, you must pay an <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/vlarel-retributies\">annual fee</a> for the supervision of the recognition. You will receive an invoice for this by post at the start of the calendar year in your name at your official address.</p><ul><li>For <strong>2023 </strong>the annual fee amounts to EUR <strong>136</strong>.</li></ul>",
